0.2 CARTE INSEE

Nous pouvons gnrer une carte du carroyage de la ville de Bondy grce la fonction : mf_map

library(mapsf)
data <- st_read("insee.gpkg", "bondy")
## Reading layer `bondy' from data source 
##   `/Users/savannahlaurent/Desktop/SIG/PROJET FINAL/script/insee.gpkg' 
##   using driver `GPKG'
## Simple feature collection with 188 features and 42 fields
## Geometry type: POLYGON
## Dimension:     XY
## Bounding box:  xmin: 661088.1 ymin: 6865338 xmax: 663354.7 ymax: 6869043
## Projected CRS: RGF93 / Lambert-93
mf_map(data, type = "choro", pal = "Burg",
       border = NA, var = "Men_pauv", leg_title = "Nb de mnages pauvres")
mf_layout(title =  "Pauvret  Bondy", credits = "INSEE Carroyage 200 m")
